column5: I always pick up my beer at the Duty Free when going in to Canada. I crossed twice last year and both times the DF at International Falls had no Canadian beer and we had to settle for Bud and Bud Light. Had I known, I could have picked up better beer locally. For those that have crossed already, does the DF at IF seem to be able to stock Canadian beer this year?
Our group got both Labatt Blue and Molson Canadian last week. Have a great time, Keith!
I think they want you to buy it at Dalseg's for 40 bucks a case !!!
